<p>This is the important part.</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">
  leftMaster = new WPI_TalonFX(1);
  rightMaster = new WPI_TalonFX(2);
  leftSlave = new WPI_TalonFX(3);
  rightSlave = new WPI_TalonFX(4);

  DifferentialDrive drive = new DifferentialDrive(leftMaster, rightSlave);
</code></pre>
<p>These should be in robotInit, not outside a method.</p>
<p>Alternately, you could do the declaration and initialization at the same time like</p>
